{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund & require all public venues to have allergy treatments including EpiPens",
        "additional_details": "In the event of a severe allergic reaction, immediate access to EpiPens or other appropriate treatments is essential. This measure could provide critical support to both children and parents during emergencies, particularly given the number of lives that have been tragically lost due to delayed treatment.",
        "background": "We want the Government to fund and require all public venues, including restaurants and shops, to be equipped with allergen medication, including EpiPens, in first aid boxes.",
